{"tid":2392792,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"攬炒巴算唔算又攬炒咗阿支奴（Ah Gi個Channel)","createTime":"2021-02-03T04:30:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T04:40:42.000Z","uid":234509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e069da99a8c9ef8a1208605471342ea18344373d","tid":2392792,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T04:30:21.000Z","msg":"中国阿支奴收受大陸資金，迫害為維吾爾族發聲嘅奧斯爾。<br />\n<br />\n中国「阿森納」本來氣勢如虹，近六場不敗<br />\n<br />\n不過，頭先有消息指阿支奴輸咗俾狼隊<br />\n<br />\n其實，攬鈔團隊同盟友一早已經準備好，狙擊阿支奴。首先，我哋攬鈔團隊收買球証，請大地雷斯食全餐<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E37xfLx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE37xfLx.png&h=e830c687&s={SIZE}\" />。跟住我哋用以毒攻毒嘅方式，利用中資狼隊攬炒阿支奴，令到敵人內訌<br />\n<br />\n我地唔係要佢「冇前四」，係直頭要佢「降班」！<br />\n<br />\n既然佢地宜家輸到仆街，我們更加要乘勝追擊，立即一人一信狂轟搞到佢哋英超降班！<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ERUvMRn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FERUvMRn.jpg&h=b9bc4dbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae3557ed15fb73154dc8c6edc686c5e78bd2f6f1","tid":2392792,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T04:36:48.000Z","msg":"呢單嘢劉祖(樓主)背後有份策劃。"},{"pid":"bede7ce272cb633f1363adef1c1766e3b3df8382","tid":2392792,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae3557ed15fb73154dc8c6edc686c5e78bd2f6f1","tid":2392792,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T04:36:48.000Z","msg":"呢單嘢劉祖(樓主)背後有份策劃。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T04:40:42.000Z","msg":"我攬炒團隊"}]}